{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312150, "create_time": 1658733201, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "不确定的话可以申欧盟的ErasmusMundus项目，全欧洲免费旅游哈哈", "timestamp": 1658733201}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312152, "create_time": 1658733276, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "上课用英语没问题。但是你去超市也用英语吗？看病也用英语吗？", "timestamp": 1658733276}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312154, "create_time": 1658733370, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "dz觉得日常生活方便吗", "timestamp": 1658733370}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312155, "create_time": 1658733394, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Alice: 完全不会芬兰语真的没问题吗？", "timestamp": 1658733394}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312157, "create_time": 1658733454, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "这说的有点too good to be true了哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1658733454}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312166, "create_time": 1658733629, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Alice: 北欧的英语普及率是很高的，润北欧最大的问题是税太高、生活成本太高、到手收入太少（相比国内互联网行业或者美国各行业）。北欧对于体力劳动者是天堂，但是有一定学历或者技能的人过去，除非真的是想躺平了，如果没有放下想赚大钱的心，肯定会在心理上有一定落差。而且北欧的生活对于习惯热闹的中国人有点boring，气候也不好。\n北欧当地人想赚大钱都是去美国，想养老都是去南欧那些气候好的地方", "timestamp": 1658733629}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312203, "create_time": 1658734915, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "本科毕业申请了阿尔托收到了全奖offer，有过依趁机移居的想法，但疫情来了加上家庭考虑，还是老老实实在国内继续卷了", "timestamp": 1658734915}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312269, "create_time": 1658738011, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 社恐很想去芬兰", "timestamp": 1658738011}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312271, "create_time": 1658738050, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "这么爽的吗", "timestamp": 1658738050}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312304, "create_time": 1658739568, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "不会当地语言融不进当地文化的。当然学会当地语言的最好方式就是融入文化....", "timestamp": 1658739568}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312376, "create_time": 1658742387, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "北欧适合没什么钱又耐得住寂寞的小镇做题家，但凡家里有点钱的去了就会感到受罪，因为你的工资和平常看不起的一般人的工资差别不大。并且你还会感到各种歧视与不便利。", "timestamp": 1658742387}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312379, "create_time": 1658742515, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "你没法用高人一等的眼光看别人，也没什么人来巴结你，和国内完全不一样。这种落差感是很强的。", "timestamp": 1658742515}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312532, "create_time": 1658748498, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "感谢洞主分享~", "timestamp": 1658748498}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312815, "create_time": 1658759591, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "去北欧留北欧是不难啊，但是北欧的好处是高福利高税收，外国人只能享受高税收没有高福利", "timestamp": 1658759591}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 314018, "create_time": 1658826437, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Kate:拿了绿卡后该有的福利都有，免费医疗，免费教育", "timestamp": 1658826437}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 314203, "create_time": 1658835887, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "洞主是赫尔辛基大学的博士嘛？", "timestamp": 1658835887}], "create_time": 1658733086, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1658835887, "likenum": 54, "n_attentions": 54, "n_comments": 16, "pid": 88323, "poll": null, "reply": 16, "text": "#88098\nt大居然有人提到芬兰，这里安利一波，非常推荐想躺平的人来北欧躺\n\n首先，申请方面，在清华倒数也基本能申到赫尔辛基大学和阿尔托大学（qs100左右），雅思和绩点不是特别垃就可。同时语言纯靠英语也没问题，芬兰语一句不会说也问题不大，上课也都是英语\n\n然后就是学费方面，虽然17年后北欧对非欧盟国家收费，但是他们奖学金特别好申，基本都能拿到a类奖学金，100%免学费，同时额外每个月发1000欧生活费，假期发3000欧旅游费用，可以说，基本一个机票费就能cover全部费用，同时北欧的生活成本也不高，而且到处都有学生优惠\n\n最后工作方面，硕士两年+工作两年就能拿到绿卡，平常暑期实习也能拿个2500欧一个月", "timestamp": 1658733086}}